

  # **Color Replacement in Image Processing**

High Level

This is a function that is part of an image processing library, likely using the Jimp package for Node.js. It allows you to replace a specific color in an image with transparency. While not explicitly shown as an exported function, it can be integrated into a larger image processing pipeline.

```javascript
